  { // push_files — multi-file commit. One file per commit is inefficient, but the tool has size limits, so batch by file size (see TURN_ENGINE.md §5). Perplexity may not auto-compact mid-turn and can crash on context overflow, so GAIA Code estimates per-turn token cost to pack work in without overflowing (TURN_ENGINE.md §2).
